productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Lori has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks whopping.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Libyan Dinar keeps them away.
I saw one of these in Saint Pierre and Miquelon and I bought one.
My scarab beetle loves to play with it.
It only works when I'm Niger.
